def palindrome_of_length_n(s):
    n = 74
    s = s.lower()

    palindromes = set()
    for i in range(len(s)-n+1):
        substring = s[i:i+n]
        if substring.isalpha() and substring == substring[::-1]:
            palindromes.add(substring)

    return palindromes
